      "content": "it's just that everything feels so pointless. i look at the calendar and i see weeks and months of this same emptiness, and i just wonder why i'm even putting in the effort to breathe. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it's like i'm already gone, just waiting for my body to catch up.",
